  dialogueGroupName: Merchant Bob
  speaker: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 162bf1a7bc06a794485c09fcb79af6f8, type: 2}
  textLine:
  - If this takes longer than a pint, I'm busy.
  - Ah, good to see an old friend - though yer barley outter diapers. What can I
    get ye?
  - Joe took me tools again. I swear, I'll bury that bastard...
  - If ye brake it, you buy it. If I break it... well, that's a traditional.
